Pagination Flow:

Initial Load: Load the first set of data when the user opens the app or navigates to a specific screen.

Next Page Trigger: Determine when to load the next page (e.g., user scrolls to the bottom of the list).

Loading Indicator: Show a loading indicator while fetching the next page.

Error Handling: Handle errors gracefully and provide a way for the user to retry.

Data Integration: Integrate new data with existing data in the list.
